  <description><![CDATA[<p>This well known mountain hotel is in a superb location at the bottom of the main slopes, just 1 minute's walk (100m) to Le Cretaz chairlift.</p>
<p>The attractive Chalet Hotel Des Guides has been part of Cervinia's history for many years, originally hosting mountaineers attempting to climb the great Matterhorn. Its central location is perfect for skiers who enjoy proximity to the piste, and the spacious lounge &amp; bar in the centre of the hotel provides a peaceful and enjoyable place to relax off the slopes. The hotel has a welcoming atmosphere where you will be well looked after by your Inghams Chalet Hotel team. Bedrooms are warm and cosy with wood clad walls, soft furnishings and en suite facilities.</p>]]></description>
